name: "I go back" by Cinthia Ponce
description:
There are so many different things in life, so many things to do,
It feels good at times and it feels hopeless. 
There are so many different things but I give them all up 
I end up giving it all up at once. And then one day I wake up and it's all gone. I go back to wanting it all in life.
